I'm sorry. I can't answer that.

05:22.920 --> 05:24.950
He was the coach of my
daughter's soccer team.

05:24.970 --> 05:27.140
Please. I'm afraid to
let her leave the house.

05:27.150 --> 05:28.760
I know this is frustrating.

05:28.770 --> 05:33.020
As soon as we get any information,
we will release it to the public.

05:34.140 --> 05:37.050
Hold tight,ok?

05:40.640 --> 05:42.440
Excuse me.

05:43.670 --> 05:46.770
William Harris, i'm
special agent derek Morgan.

05:46.790 --> 05:48.980
This is special agent david Rossi.

05:48.990 --> 05:51.860
Before you,uh, answer any questions,

05:51.870 --> 05:55.240
I need to remind you that you're
entitled to have a lawyer present.

05:55.270 --> 05:57.690
I am a lawyer.

06:02.710 --> 06:04.960
She look familiar to you?

06:07.130 --> 06:09.240
How 'bout her?

06:12.800 --> 06:15.630
Her? No?

06:16.550 --> 06:19.120
The three of these girls were
raped,strangled, and dumped.

06:19.130 --> 06:22.740
My god. I have a daughter their age.

06:23.820 --> 06:26.050
Missy Dewald. She
went missing yesterday.

06:26.060 --> 06:28.670
What do you think you have on me?

06:29.380 --> 06:33.090
We have a witness who can place you at
the mall the same time of her abduction.

06:33.100 --> 06:37.180
And,uh,well, rumor has it that you seem
to have a history of this type of behavior.

06:37.200 --> 06:38.200
How is that?

06:38.210 --> 06:40.090
Tell us about Atlanta.

06:40.110 --> 06:44.440
Atlanta? Those charges were
dropped. It was a mistake.

06:44.450 --> 06:50.800
Because the 2 rape victims wouldn't testify,
and now you cover your tracks by killing them.

06:52.210 --> 06:54.700
I didn't do this.

06:54.710 --> 06:59.550
So,William,you've been
married,what,18 years?

06:59.570 --> 07:03.510
You remember that feeling
you get when you fall in love?

07:03.530 --> 07:09.960
All those firsts-- the kiss, the
smell of her hair-- it's exciting.

07:10.350 --> 07:13.800
You miss that feeling, don't you?

07:14.330 --> 07:20.690
Being married to the same woman, it's
like ordering the same entree for 18 years.

07:20.700 --> 07:24.700
Agent Rossi,every
minute you spend with me

07:24.710 --> 07:27.570
is another minute she's alone with him.

07:27.580 --> 07:30.290
So we've brought in the wrong guy?

07:30.300 --> 07:31.250
Yes.

07:31.280 --> 07:33.010
Just like they did in Atlanta.

07:33.030 --> 07:34.450
Yes.

07:34.470 --> 07:37.360
And by the time you realize
i've been telling the truth...

07:39.030 --> 07:42.620
This poor girl could be dead.

07:47.830 --> 07:50.020
Would you prefer to do this alone?

07:50.040 --> 07:52.860
Uh,this may be too
disturbing for your daughter.

07:54.650 --> 07:57.110
It's ok. We have no secrets.

07:57.120 --> 07:59.700
Can you account for William's
whereabouts for the last 24 hours?

07:59.710 --> 08:01.670
My dad was at home with us.

08:01.690 --> 08:02.930
The whole time?

08:02.960 --> 08:06.790
He may have ran out for about an
hour or so. I really don't rember.

08:06.800 --> 08:08.970
3 girls have been murdered, Mrs. Harris.

08:08.990 --> 08:11.770
Missy Dewald is missing now,
and she's running out of time.

08:11.780 --> 08:13.110
That's not my fault.

08:13.140 --> 08:15.840
How would you feel if
someone was hurting Andrea?

08:16.460 --> 08:18.280
Why did you move to
florida 6 months ago?

08:18.300 --> 08:20.540
My dad got a better
offer with another firm.

08:20.560 --> 08:23.010
It had nothing to do with
the rape charges in Atlanta?

08:23.020 --> 08:24.550
Those charges were dropped.

08:24.580 --> 08:28.010
Do you really think it's a coincidence
your husband's been a suspect twice?

08:28.020 --> 08:32.309
It was a mistake, just like this.

08:32.900 --> 08:35.179
Has William been distant lately?

08:35.200 --> 08:36.980
Spent a lot of time behind closed doors?

08:36.990 --> 08:40.400
He works a lot. Is that a crime?

08:40.409 --> 08:45.920
I think you've known something
is off, and it's made you wonder.

08:46.440 --> 08:48.880
It's something only you would know.

08:48.890 --> 08:52.420
Mrs. Harris,you can
save Missy Dewald's life,

08:52.430 --> 08:54.920
in spite of what's
happening in your family.

08:58.500 --> 09:01.930
That's enough. This interview is over.

09:08.780 --> 09:09.820
You find anything?

09:09.850 --> 09:11.980
Give me a minute. I will find the grime.

09:11.990 --> 09:14.490
All right. You ready to
start searching his computer?

09:14.500 --> 09:16.460
Born ready.

09:18.770 --> 09:20.140
Seem to be in control.

09:20.150 --> 09:22.170
i'm always in control, sweet cheeks.

09:22.190 --> 09:25.050
So far,William Harris appears
to be quite intelligent.

09:25.080 --> 09:27.050
He's covering his tracks pretty well.

09:27.080 --> 09:29.130
Yeah,just because you
delete your history,

09:29.160 --> 09:33.430
It doesn't mean all your dirty cyberlaundry isn't
hanging out there for me to find on your hard drive.

09:33.460 --> 09:35.570
Rookie mistake.

09:38.240 --> 09:39.350
William.

09:39.360 --> 09:41.590
- Keep moving,sir.
- Bailiff...

09:41.600 --> 09:44.370
Mr. Harris can have a few
moments with his family.

09:45.400 --> 09:47.150
- Dad.
- Honey.

09:48.710 --> 09:49.820
How's my girl?

09:49.830 --> 09:51.290
I'll be fine once you're home.

09:51.300 --> 09:54.690
I'm workin' on that. How you doin'?

09:55.030 --> 09:56.930
I know. Believe me,I know.

09:56.940 --> 09:59.280
But,uh, they don't have a case.

09:59.300 --> 10:02.610
Honey,bail was set at $5
million. They must have something.

10:02.620 --> 10:03.920
Well,after Atlanta...

10:03.950 --> 10:07.650
Ok,so what should I do? Should I
pull money from the retirement fund?

10:07.660 --> 10:10.610
- Just use the house.
- The house?

10:10.620 --> 10:12.390
Honey,where are we gonna
go if something happens?

10:12.400 --> 10:15.010
- Everything is gonna be fine.
- Mr. Harris.

10:15.020 --> 10:18.000
- I have to go. Look after your mom for me.
- I will.

10:18.010 --> 10:20.730
I need you to be
strong. I love you both.

10:20.740 --> 10:26.550
We love you,too,honey. Thank you.

10:28.870 --> 10:32.300
Did you see how Sharon reacted
when he said to put up the house?

10:32.320 --> 10:34.460
She's starting to doubt him.

10:34.470 --> 10:36.170
Garcia's been digging
through William's computer.

10:36.190 --> 10:38.690
She found an encrypted
link to a web page.

10:38.710 --> 10:39.480
Where'd it take you?

10:39.510 --> 10:42.850
Uh,an unsearchable, untraceable
blog with tons of journal entries.

10:42.860 --> 10:44.190
It's like some sort of diary.

10:44.200 --> 10:45.520
You find anything incriminating?

10:45.540 --> 10:48.510
I was able to differentiate between
2 distinct voices, 2 authors.

10:48.540 --> 10:51.280
I found various idiosyncratic
words, phrases,punctuation,

10:51.300 --> 10:54.210
And orthography within the blog entries
consistent with each separate person--

10:54.230 --> 10:55.780
Words like "soda" and "pop."

10:55.800 --> 10:58.870
One guy uses dashes while
the other uses ellipses.

11:00.870 --> 11:02.760
Where'd you find this kid?

11:02.770 --> 11:05.850
He was left in a basket
on the steps of the F.B.I.

11:05.860 --> 11:09.870
One side of the discourse made
a reference to the devil's strip.

11:09.880 --> 11:10.870
What the hell's that?

11:10.890 --> 11:14.000
Uh,it's a small patch of grass that
separates the sidewalk from the street.

11:14.020 --> 11:16.380
Now,that term is only
used in central ohio.

11:16.390 --> 11:19.240
William lived in Atlanta for 20
years, but he grew up in columbus.

11:19.250 --> 11:22.620
The other guy uses words like
"turnpike" and "filling the gas tank,"

11:22.640 --> 11:25.330
Both specific regionalisms for florida.

11:26.720 --> 11:30.530
Kid,you sure about this? Right.

11:32.250 --> 11:34.760
Was there a new development?

11:34.770 --> 11:37.990
"can't rember the last time I
smiled for so long that it hurt.

11:38.000 --> 11:40.280
I've never felt like this before."

11:40.330 --> 11:42.260
Sounds like you're bored at home.

11:42.270 --> 11:43.770
Havin' an affair?

11:43.780 --> 11:46.880
I told you i'm happily married.

11:46.890 --> 11:49.750
Does your wife know
about your secret diary?

11:49.770 --> 11:52.280
I bet she'd like to know how
good you are at keeping secrets.

11:52.310 --> 11:54.380
I'm not sure what you
think you've found,

11:54.400 --> 11:58.580
But you've gone from completely
wrong to completely insane.

11:58.590 --> 11:59.850
You're hiding something,William.

11:59.860 --> 12:04.140
No jury will convict me because
somebody saw me at the mall

12:04.160 --> 12:07.920
And you think i'm talking with
someone other than my wife.

12:10.130 --> 12:12.330
We found Missy.

12:12.340 --> 12:13.890
Told you so.

12:13.910 --> 12:15.280
You son of a bitch!

12:15.290 --> 12:18.990
- Detective,no!
- Damn you!

12:23.160 --> 12:26.090
That's her. That's Missy.

12:26.100 --> 12:29.410
I looked her father in the eye
and swore i'd find her alive.

12:29.710 --> 12:32.850
So since we've been here,this girl's
gone missing and now turned up dead.

12:32.860 --> 12:35.530
Do you think he dumped the
body before he was picked up?

12:35.540 --> 12:38.210
The m.e.estimates she was
killed several hours ago.

12:38.220 --> 12:40.800
But we've had William Harris in custody.

12:41.380 --> 12:42.780
You think we have the wrong guy?

12:42.790 --> 12:43.910
I don't think so.

12:43.930 --> 12:45.710
He's communicating with someone.

12:45.720 --> 12:47.790
He's confident they
won't turn against him.

12:47.800 --> 12:50.340
I don't think he's having an affair.

12:50.350 --> 12:51.660
He has a partner.

12:51.690 --> 12:55.190
And that partner's doing everything
he can to get Harris out of jail.

13:00.070 --> 13:03.390
"I love the challenges..." "the
only suspense for tonight..."

13:03.400 --> 13:06.110
"was tough,but I figured it
out..." "perfect timing..."

13:06.120 --> 13:08.760
"I watch them chase
their little spawns..."

13:08.770 --> 13:12.670
"...passage truly.those
first few hours are the best."

13:12.680 --> 13:16.120
"faith should never be broken."

13:17.090 --> 13:19.190
Tell me you found his partner.

13:19.700 --> 13:21.100
Reid.

13:21.110 --> 13:23.740
It's all so cryptic.

13:26.690 --> 13:29.280
"the end of the day came too soon."

13:29.300 --> 13:31.510
Well,they clearly
enjoyed being together.

13:31.520 --> 13:35.300
They wrote a cluster of others right after
the first victim, kim groves,Was killed.

13:35.310 --> 13:36.850
we need to figure out how they met.

13:36.880 --> 13:38.990
There's gotta be something in
all this about their courtship.

13:39.000 --> 13:43.040
"it all seemed so hopeless, but I
finally learned to rise above it."

13:43.070 --> 13:45.560
It sounds like William confessed
he was feeling incomplete.

13:45.570 --> 13:46.800
He was.

13:46.820 --> 13:49.320
He didn't start killing
until he met his soul mate.

13:49.340 --> 13:51.650
"faith should never be broken."

13:51.670 --> 13:54.810
The longer they got away with it,
the stronger their relationship.

13:55.550 --> 13:57.710
Sounds like these two aren't just
obsessed with rape and murder.

13:57.720 --> 13:59.930
They're addicted to one another.

14:00.570 --> 14:01.990
We could have saved her.

14:02.010 --> 14:05.050
There were no signs of his
having a partner until now.

14:05.060 --> 14:06.710
I guess that's why he's so cocky.

14:06.720 --> 14:09.110
Well,his arrogance is typical
of a dominant personality.

14:09.120 --> 14:11.360
He's found a submissive
who's willing to kill for him.

14:11.390 --> 14:12.750
The partner is a biter.

14:12.770 --> 14:14.980
We found marks on Missy Dewald.

14:14.990 --> 14:16.290
They never did that before.

14:16.300 --> 14:18.430
Well,with William out of the
picture, he's changed his behavior.

14:18.450 --> 14:22.410
Maybe the partner went back to something
that's comfortable, something he's done before.

14:22.420 --> 14:25.770
I've got Garcia checking dental
records against other cases.

14:30.220 --> 14:32.510
D.A.was ready to charge him
when Missy was still alive.

14:32.520 --> 14:34.710
How the hell are we
supposed to keep him now?

14:38.070 --> 14:41.380
I'm surprised you're writing
all this stuff to a fella.

14:41.390 --> 14:44.360
Sounds like you have a
real special thing goin' on.

14:44.390 --> 14:46.330
I mean,i'm thinkin' if the
two of you had just got it on,

14:46.370 --> 14:48.720
Maybe these women would still be alive.

14:48.740 --> 14:50.390
So where'd you meet him?

14:50.410 --> 14:52.930
Chat room? Porn sites? Gay bar?

14:52.940 --> 14:56.560
Whoever this guy is, he's lookin'
out for you, cleaned up for you.

14:56.840 --> 14:58.210
Missy Dewald is dead.

14:58.250 --> 14:59.910
Has he called yet?

14:59.930 --> 15:02.520
Lee jarvis,the D.A.

15:02.540 --> 15:04.670
I saw his name on the warrant.

15:04.680 --> 15:08.020
He's got the best
conviction rate in florida.

15:08.040 --> 15:09.580
Do you know why?

15:09.610 --> 15:12.930
I wanna know why your pen pal killed
her when he could have let her rot.

15:12.950 --> 15:15.360
Jarvis doesn't like to lose.

15:15.370 --> 15:18.570
He's not gonna ruin
his record over this.

15:18.590 --> 15:21.870
Wow, this friend of yours wants
to please you bad,doesn't he?

15:21.900 --> 15:26.100
Oh,he is protecting you, doin' whatever he's
gotta do to make sure that you're innocent.

15:26.130 --> 15:28.570
He killed Missy so you
could be together again.

15:28.600 --> 15:32.650
It's only been a few
hours, but he misses you.

15:32.660 --> 15:35.800
And you've gotten what
exactly from all this?

15:35.830 --> 15:39.340
Proof that someone out
there is just as sick as you.

15:40.670 --> 15:43.740
It turns out there's a lot of
sick pups in central florida.

15:43.770 --> 15:46.330
Today's dental records do
not match William Harris,

15:46.360 --> 15:49.660
But do match a reported rape in
manatee county earlier this year.

15:49.690 --> 15:50.970
That's great. You got a match.

15:50.980 --> 15:52.670
Yeah,the teeth belong
to the same person,

15:52.700 --> 15:55.030
But they've never been arrested,so
I can't cross-reference.

15:55.050 --> 15:56.140
What about the victim?

15:56.180 --> 15:59.580
Connie mayers. She
still lives in the area.

16:00.580 --> 16:04.590
They're gonna ask who
you are. They don't know.

16:05.350 --> 16:08.390
- We're just buying flowers.
- Those daisies are nice.

16:08.400 --> 16:13.550
In your report,uh, it says your attacker
knew what he wanted, that he was confident.

16:13.570 --> 16:15.460
More like a control freak.

16:15.480 --> 16:19.190
He wore a mask, but I
could tell he was white.

