2 were born and raised
in the sunshine state.

33:54.760 --> 33:56.350
One is on disability.

33:56.380 --> 33:58.670
One owns a real estate business.

33:58.680 --> 34:00.330
Oh,my god. He lives right next door.

34:00.340 --> 34:02.350
Steven baleman.

34:09.320 --> 34:12.300
Steven baleman.

34:39.810 --> 34:43.020
Are you following me? Are you?

34:47.199 --> 34:48.900
He was angry and just took off.

34:48.920 --> 34:51.260
- Why was he upset?
- He's been like this all day.

34:51.270 --> 34:54.139
- When did it start?
- I don't know.

34:54.150 --> 34:55.560
This morning.

34:55.590 --> 34:59.520
So after William was arrested, he
became hostile, didn't he,nervous?

34:59.550 --> 35:01.300
Steven is a good man.

35:01.330 --> 35:03.630
He's not who you think he is.

35:05.060 --> 35:08.220
Andrea. Andrea.

35:08.230 --> 35:10.800
- Did you see Andrea out here?
- No.

35:11.880 --> 35:13.500
Why is annie crying?

35:13.510 --> 35:15.790
We think that Steven
is William's accomplice.

35:15.800 --> 35:16.800
Where's Steven?

35:16.820 --> 35:19.360
- We're trying to figure that out.
- Oh,my god.

35:19.650 --> 35:23.580
Andrea said it was strange
that he was the only nice one.

35:23.590 --> 35:26.180
He was checking in on us.

35:26.210 --> 35:28.480
I wasn't listening. I'm sorry.

35:28.490 --> 35:30.430
Now they're both gone.

35:30.450 --> 35:32.780
It's time you talked to William.

35:34.140 --> 35:36.790
No,Steven baleman is
not just your neighbor.

35:36.800 --> 35:38.050
And you know this how?

35:38.060 --> 35:39.860
You told us.

35:39.870 --> 35:41.690
Those don't prove anything.

35:41.700 --> 35:46.900
And after all this time, you figuring out who
my neighbor is feels like a really small victory.

35:51.930 --> 35:54.440
Where did Steven take Andrea?

35:54.930 --> 35:56.950
Wh-what are you talkin' about?

35:56.970 --> 36:00.660
She suspected him, and
now they're both missing.

36:00.720 --> 36:03.440
How could you? She believed you.

36:03.450 --> 36:05.190
Th-they're missing?

36:05.210 --> 36:08.070
All those times you disappeared,
i knew it wasn't work.

36:08.090 --> 36:12.890
i thought maybe, maybe
you were having an affair,

36:12.900 --> 36:16.520
And I couldn't confront you,because
then that would make it real.

36:17.400 --> 36:21.230
Then i'd have to find the
truth buried in your lies,

36:21.240 --> 36:24.870
And you have been paid
to lie for so long.

36:24.900 --> 36:26.550
It is who you are!

36:26.560 --> 36:31.760
Look,all of this is almost too much.
It's too much for anybody to put up with.

36:31.770 --> 36:34.210
But it's almost over.

36:34.230 --> 36:36.510
I didn't put up the house.

36:38.050 --> 36:40.900
You--you didn't
post bail?

36:41.400 --> 36:44.470
I didn't wanna believe it in Atlanta,
and i'm not gonna deny it again.

36:44.490 --> 36:48.040
Now,where did Steven take Andrea?

36:48.670 --> 36:52.860
Where is she? Where is...

36:54.150 --> 36:58.610
You son of a--
you son of a bitch!

37:06.300 --> 37:08.080
How'd that feel, William?

37:08.090 --> 37:10.430
You see what you're doin'?

37:11.560 --> 37:16.180
Kim groves,your words-- "the
first few hours are the best.

37:16.220 --> 37:19.040
Nobody's run out of steam yet."

37:19.070 --> 37:23.460
Andrea's been gone for 2 hours.

37:23.500 --> 37:27.000
What's he doing to her right now?

37:27.030 --> 37:30.440
What is he doin', William? Touchin' her?

37:31.190 --> 37:32.960
Maybe he's bitin' her,huh?

37:32.980 --> 37:35.760
This is what he does
when you're not around.

37:35.770 --> 37:40.180
Your little boyfriend is twisted,
and now he's got your baby girl.

37:40.200 --> 37:41.950
You know better than us.

37:41.990 --> 37:45.900
Has she been in pain this whole time?

37:46.410 --> 37:48.440
Steven took your daughter.

37:48.470 --> 37:52.740
The man you trusted with
your life has betrayed you.

37:53.380 --> 37:56.470
What,is nothin' sacred to you?

38:00.890 --> 38:04.150
So Steven baleman has a couple of commercial
properties, but so far,there's nothing.

38:04.180 --> 38:06.550
Only he knows where Steven took Andrea.

38:06.560 --> 38:09.820
I can't believe he sold out his
daughter to protect his partner.

38:09.850 --> 38:12.000
He's protecting himself.

38:12.010 --> 38:14.240
The minute he says
anything, he's guilty.

38:14.270 --> 38:16.670
What was it you said about Missy,hmm?

38:16.700 --> 38:19.660
Man,turn around and look at me!

38:20.880 --> 38:24.550
For every minute that goes
by, he's alone with her,right?

38:24.980 --> 38:28.050
Well,it's Andrea's turn now.

38:28.060 --> 38:29.410
What is wrong with you,man?

38:29.430 --> 38:32.300
Why aren't you tryin' to run out
that door and save your child?

38:32.330 --> 38:34.570
You think he's not gonna hurt her? Why?

38:34.580 --> 38:38.390
Did you make some kind of
deal? Family's off-limits?

38:38.400 --> 38:42.430
The longer you are in here,
the worse it looked for Steven.

38:42.440 --> 38:45.330
He think you're in here betraying
him, so now he's actin' out.

38:45.350 --> 38:46.690
He's lost faith.

38:46.730 --> 38:50.370
He is alone with your little girl.

38:51.020 --> 38:55.060
She's probably cryin' out for you,
sayin',"daddy,daddy, why aren't you helpin' me?"

38:55.080 --> 38:58.590
Why? Because you're
standin' here, doin' nothin'.

39:02.920 --> 39:04.220
William...

39:04.250 --> 39:07.190
You're the only person
who can stop this.

39:08.290 --> 39:12.650
Be a man. For god sakes, be a father.

39:20.750 --> 39:22.870
Andrea!

39:25.920 --> 39:28.590
- Oh,dad,thank god.
- You're gonna be ok.

39:28.600 --> 39:30.040
It's Steven. It's Steven.

39:30.050 --> 39:31.460
I don't know where
he went. I don't know.

39:31.470 --> 39:33.470
I'm gonna get you out of here.

39:36.190 --> 39:38.890
- Did he hurt you?
- Did you think i'd hurt her?

39:38.900 --> 39:41.230
That i'd betray you?

39:41.240 --> 39:44.150
Or is that because
that's what you did to me?

39:44.160 --> 39:46.930
I didn't tell them anything.

39:48.380 --> 39:52.120
You didn't tell them anything?
Dad,what are you talking about?

39:52.130 --> 39:54.740
Wait. How did you even
know that I was here?

39:54.750 --> 39:57.080
Andrea,honey, trust me.

39:57.140 --> 40:00.090
Daddy's gonna make it ok. Ok?

40:01.150 --> 40:02.270
We had a deal.

40:02.290 --> 40:04.500
Faith should never be broken.

40:04.530 --> 40:07.710
- You took my daughter!
- She followed me here!

40:08.330 --> 40:11.200
She never would have said anything.

40:11.970 --> 40:14.750
I never would have said anything?

40:15.620 --> 40:19.060
Honey, Andrea,please.

40:19.070 --> 40:22.230
Just--just trust
me. Trust me,ok?

40:22.240 --> 40:24.840
So how'd you get out?

40:26.490 --> 40:29.190
Uh,the case-- the
case was dismissed.

40:29.210 --> 40:31.960
Oh,really? Simple as that?

40:31.970 --> 40:34.110
You killed msy Dewald
while I was in custody.

40:34.140 --> 40:35.670
They didn't have enough to hold me.

40:35.680 --> 40:36.890
He talked about Missy. We got him.

40:36.900 --> 40:39.700
So he killed Missy Dewald, and what?

40:39.730 --> 40:41.910
What? You killed all the others?

40:41.920 --> 40:44.510
- Honey,please.
- No.

40:44.520 --> 40:47.090
Don't--don't
come close to me.

40:47.100 --> 40:50.430
I had your back.

40:51.050 --> 40:54.290
What were you gonna do?
What if I hadn't shown up?

40:54.300 --> 40:57.050
Were you gonna kill her?

41:01.440 --> 41:03.960
- F.B.I.!
- Don't move! You're under arrest!

41:03.970 --> 41:06.350
Don't even think about it!

41:12.390 --> 41:15.100
Andrea. Andrea.

41:39.960 --> 41:41.960
Mom. Mom,get me out of
here. Get me out of here.

41:41.970 --> 41:43.780
Ok. You're gonna be ok.

41:43.790 --> 41:47.270
- I wanna go away,ok?
- Ok. I promise,baby.

41:49.600 --> 41:52.620
The guy wanted just to
see his partner again.

41:52.630 --> 41:55.370
They needed to say good-bye.

41:55.380 --> 41:59.790
Those two had everything figured
out except how it would end.

